asset.author: Hoover
asset.hookText: If your Hoover Air vacuum is experiencing a loss of suction, or doesn't seem to be picking up as well as when you first got the cleaner, we can help! This short video will walk you through some easy steps to get your WindTunnel Air vacuum sucking up dirt and grime as well as the first day you got it.
